OL,6,FOne of Wales' most notorious murderers
OL,7,Fis set to be released from prison on
OL,8,Flicence after a decision by the Parole
OL,9,FBoard.
OL,11,FJeffrey Gafoor was sentenced to life
OL,12,Fin 2003 after advances in DNA
OL,13,Ftechnology linked him with the 1988
OL,14,FValentine's Day murder of Lynette
OL,15,FWhite, 20, who was stabbed more than
OL,16,F50 times at her docklands flat in
OL,17,FCardiff.
