OL,3,CLynette White murderer Jeffrey Gafoor
OL,4,Cto be released from prison
OL,6,FGafoor was jailed for life with a
OL,7,Fminimum of 13 years at Cardiff Crown
OL,8,FCourt in 2003 after pleading guilty to
OL,9,Fmurder when he was 38, confessing to
OL,10,Fstabbing Ms White with a knife more
OL,11,Fthan 50 times following a row over #30.
OL,13,FThe Parole Board said: "After
OL,14,Fconsidering the circumstances of his
OL,15,Foffending, the progress made while in
OL,16,Fcustody and the other evidence
OL,17,Fpresented at the hearing, the panel
OL,18,Fwas satisfied that imprisonment was no
OL,19,Flonger necessary for the protection of
OL,20,Fthe public."
