OL,6,FAccording to a summary of the
OL,7,Fdecision, at the time of his crimes
OL,8,FGafoor had a "willingness to use
OL,9,Fextreme violence", "lacked emotional
OL,10,Fcontrol" in stressful situations and
OL,11,Fhad anger problems. He would also
OL,12,F"ruminate about events and hold
OL,13,Fgrudges against people".
OL,15,FBut the panel said his behaviour in
OL,16,Fprison had been "very good" and there
OL,17,Fwas no evidence of violence in custody.
