OL,6,FThe document said: "During the course
OL,7,Fof four years in two different open
OL,8,Festablishments, he had successfully
OL,9,Fcompleted temporary releases from
OL,10,Fprison. The official supervising his
OL,11,Fcase in prison described for the panel
OL,12,Fhow well Mr Gaffoor had managed
OL,13,Fdifficult situations."
