OL,10,Fconditions following an oral hearing
OL,11,Fheld in October 2024.
OL,13,F"This is his sixth review by the
OL,14,FParole Board since the end of the
OL,15,Fminimum tariff period set by the
OL,16,Fsentencing judge, which expired in
OL,17,F2016.
