OL,6,FAt Gafoor's sentencing, Patrick
OL,7,FHarrington QC, prosecuting, told the
OL,8,Fcourt: "He did not simply kill, he
OL,9,Fattacked in a barbaric manner,
OL,10,Fcutting, stabbing and slashing his
OL,11,Fvictim over 50 times, cutting her
OL,12,Fthroat, slashing both wrists, cutting,
OL,13,Fstabbing and slashing her face, arm
OL,14,Fand especially the torso.
OL,16,F"It is tempting to talk of the
OL,17,Fdefendant having attacked in a frenzy,
OL,18,Fbut the pattern of distribution of
OL,19,Finjuries suggests a particular
OL,20,Fmindset."
